{"tid":2042897,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"兩個女生 - 陳惜姿","createTime":"2020-05-30T05:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T06:38:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f09eb359e7b2e09a6926850118a1f483c6d13a","tid":2042897,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:16:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E6%83%9C%E5%A7%BF/daily/article/20200530/20927384/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2583%259C%25E5%25A7%25BF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200530%2F20927384%2F&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=cbd375a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2583%259C%25E5%25A7%25BF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200530%2F20927384%2F&h=4f8fe409\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E6%83%9C%E5%A7%BF/daily/article/20200530/20927384/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩個女生 - 陳惜姿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200530/large/1590735359_4cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200530%2Flarge%2F1590735359_4cda.jpg&h=7c95ea57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n看到一個新聞鏡頭，很多母親受不了&mdash;&mdash;反國歌法多區示威當天，亦是中三至中五生復課首日。被抓上警車的人裏，有兩個穿着白色校服裙的女生，特別顯眼。她們戴了眼鏡，束着馬尾，背個大書包，校裙過膝，一雙白襪，襪頭一邊高、一邊低。她們這個模樣，更像是要到學校附近的文具店，尋找那色彩繽紛的顏色螢光筆，在試紙上寫寫畫畫。<br />\n<br />\n其中一人個子不高，若非中一二生仍在停課，人們還以為她是中一生。校裙很長，是母親認為她還會長高，特意買大碼，所有母親都這樣想。這種樸素女生，我們常常遇到，家裏或者都有。儘管我們不知香港以後如何走下去，這仍是下一代的將來，他們仍會在這裏成長，盼着如七彩螢光筆一樣的斑斕人生。然而她們不是去文具店，而是被抓去警局。<br />\n<br />\n我們回憶初中，會想到精品店裏心愛但買不起的小掛飾，信和中心貼滿明星相的小舖，和唱片店裏翻來覆去始終捨不得買的卡式帶。那是寒傖青澀的回憶，物質貧乏卻也無憂。這一代的年輕人，背上過份沉重的時代，成長記憶也不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n當天被捕者396人，四成是學生，80人未成年，年紀最小的12歲。幾多人勸他們不要再「送頭」，他們仍是前仆後繼。看到這裏，除了心痛、流淚，也很無力。有人說要放棄這一代的年輕人，但我們不會。 <br />\n<br />\n陳惜姿<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949c70daa8d0fecf147f985398568a0725a444f5","tid":2042897,"uid":342828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"所以D黑警比人睇小係自取其辱。濫捕到連咁嘅學生妹都唔放過，只會比人恥笑你係無知兼低能，而唔係覺得你真係做到所謂嘅「止暴制亂」。不過諗呢條橋嗰個應該都會有得升官發財嘅，因為佢已經證咗自己嘅質素同佢嘅上司不相上下（咁低）。"},{"pid":"e352891e07603c6bf4a031e7887ce2641d3b99d4","tid":2042897,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5180e91191707dabd5968377232575ec1f4ddb75","tid":2042897,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":